---
const upgrades = [
  { name: "Kioto Esencial", price: "$2,490 MXN", image: "/images/tunel-sagrado.webp" },
  { name: "Nara, Kobe e Himeji", price: "$3,150 MXN", image: "/images/templo-antiguo.webp" },
  { name: "Show de Sumo y Cena Chanko Nabe", price: "$1,890 MXN", image: "/images/chanko.webp" },
  { name: "Experiencia Wakayama", price: "$2,200 MXN", image: "/images/wakayama.webp" },
  { name: "El Sagrado Monte Fuji", price: "$1,950 MXN", image: "/images/fuji.webp" }
];
---

<section class="py-24 bg-gray-900 text-white overflow-hidden relative">
  <!-- Decorative Background -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-japan-red/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -mr-48 -mt-48"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-japan-coral/5 rounded-full blur-3xl -ml-48 -mb-48"></div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 relative z-10">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">
        HAZ TU VIAJE TODAVÍA <span class="text-japan-red">MÁS TUYO</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Elige las experiencias premium que quieras sumar a tu itinerario.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      {upgrades.map(item => (
        <div class="bg-gray-800/50 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl border border-white/10 hover:border-japan-red transition-all group overflow-hidden flex flex-col">
          <div class="h-40 overflow-hidden opacity-60 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <img src={item.image} alt={item.name} class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="p-8">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-japan-red transition-colors">{item.name}</h3>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-japan-coral">{item.price}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <p class="text-center mt-12 text-gray-500 text-sm italic">
      Nota: Los precios en pesos son informativos y calculados bajo el tipo de cambio vigente al momento de su liquidación.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
